INSERT INTO
          tokens (
            l1_token_address,
            l2_token_address,
            name,
            symbol,
            decimals,
            l2_block_number,
            initialization_transaction,
            usd_price
          )
        VALUES
          ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8) ON CONFLICT (l1_token_address, l2_token_address) DO NOTHING
